<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How would you feel about a girl
who liked to drive the passes</b></font>

158
00:10:29,734 --> 00:10:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and acted like a street racer?</b></font>

159
00:10:37,414 --> 00:10:39,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--A Sileighty?!
--Yes.</b></font>

160
00:10:39,744 --> 00:10:42,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They say a blue Sileighty is the fastest now.</b></font>

161
00:10:42,514 --> 00:10:46,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And surprisingly, its driver is a woman.</b></font>

162
00:10:46,384 --> 00:10:48,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A woman?!</b></font>

163
00:10:49,524 --> 00:10:53,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--A female racer...
--Yes...</b></font>

164
00:10:53,324 --> 00:10:56,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm totally okay with it, really.</b></font>

165
00:10:56,834 --> 00:11:01,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As a matter of fact, I'd feel more
comfortable if she were a racer.</b></font>

166
00:11:01,004 --> 00:11:03,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Really?
--Yeah.</b></font>

167
00:11:04,774 --> 00:11:07,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now I get it.</i></b></font>

168
00:11:07,274 --> 00:11:09,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>She wants to be a racer,</i></b></font>

169
00:11:09,914 --> 00:11:13,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>which is why she likes an FC.</i></b></font>

170
00:11:13,344 --> 00:11:15,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A Sileighty with a woman driver.</b></font>

171
00:11:15,854 --> 00:11:18,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A Sileighty...?</b></font>

172
00:11:18,024 --> 00:11:20,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Is that an import?
--No.</b></font>

173
00:11:20,624 --> 00:11:25,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a 180 with a Silvia front end on it.</b></font>

174
00:11:25,264 --> 00:11:29,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Silvia and 180, so "Sileighty."</b></font>

175
00:11:30,734 --> 00:11:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Its driver is the fastest at Usui Pass,</b></font>

176
00:11:34,234 --> 00:11:36,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and is a woman.</b></font>

177
00:11:36,234 --> 00:11:38,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I gotta see that!</b></font>

178
00:11:38,244 --> 00:11:41,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can see her there at night, usually.</b></font>

179
00:11:41,874 --> 00:11:45,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not wise to challenge her, though.</b></font>

180
00:11:45,384 --> 00:11:48,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No locals even come close to her.</b></font>

181
00:12:05,264 --> 00:12:07,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's called Akina Speed Stars.</b></font>

182
00:12:07,934 --> 00:12:10,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I built the team.</b></font>

183
00:12:10,504 --> 00:12:13,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have a young racer who they say</b></font>

184
00:12:13,644 --> 00:12:15,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is the fastest at Akina Pass.</b></font>

185
00:12:15,614 --> 00:12:19,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Speed-wise, I'd say I'm right behind him.</b></font>

186
00:12:19,484 --> 00:12:21,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's wrong, Mako?</b></font>

187
00:12:21,654 --> 00:12:23,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it's nothing.</b></font>

188
00:12:23,984 --> 00:12:28,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, I must be boring you with my car talk.</b></font>

189
00:12:28,654 --> 00:12:30,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it's not that.</b></font>

190
00:12:30,964 --> 00:12:34,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I love cars, too, so it's fun.</b></font>

191
00:12:34,594 --> 00:12:37,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really? I'm glad.</b></font>

192
00:12:39,504 --> 00:12:45,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, do you also admire great
drifting skills and all that?</b></font>

193
00:12:45,274 --> 00:12:46,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure.</b></font>

194
00:12:46,444 --> 00:12:49,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You need a lot of experience, like I have,</b></font>

195
00:12:49,874 --> 00:12:51,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to use that technique, though.</b></font>

196
00:12:51,544 --> 00:12:54,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's dangerous.</b></font>

197
00:12:54,454 --> 00:12:57,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, you're good at drifting?</b></font>

198
00:12:57,054 --> 00:13:00,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Sure.
--I'm happy for you!</b></font>

199
00:13:00,684 --> 00:13:02,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah?</b></font>

200
00:13:10,164 --> 00:13:13,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you for a wonderful day.</b></font>

201
00:13:14,374 --> 00:13:17,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--So, Mako...
--Yes?</b></font>

202
00:13:17,844 --> 00:13:21,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I'm wondering if you have...</b></font>

203
00:13:21,544 --> 00:13:25,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...you know, someone...</b></font>

204
00:13:25,184 --> 00:13:27,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...you're seeing right now.</b></font>

205
00:13:29,384 --> 00:13:32,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't have a boyfriend.</b></font>

206
00:13:33,854 --> 00:13:38,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, call me again, Iketani.</b></font>

207
00:13:42,834 --> 00:13:46,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Wow!</i></b></font>

208
00:13:47,674 --> 00:13:50,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can you hear me, Iketani?</b></font>

209
00:13:50,904 --> 00:13:53,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wake up, Iketani.</b></font>

210
00:13:55,274 --> 00:13:57,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, I'm...</b></font>

211
00:13:58,844 --> 00:14:00,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why are you here?!</b></font>

212
00:14:00,244 --> 00:14:04,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We couldn't go back, 'cause
we were worried about you.</b></font>

213
00:14:04,354 --> 00:14:07,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, how did it go?</b></font>

214
00:14:09,554 --> 00:14:12,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Today was a fine day, indeed.</b></font>

215
00:14:12,624 --> 00:14:16,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You hungry? Dinner's on me!</b></font>

216
00:14:16,634 --> 00:14:19,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can also check out</b></font>

217
00:14:19,704 --> 00:14:21,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the racers at Usui Pass.</b></font>

218
00:14:21,574 --> 00:14:24,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sounds like it went well.</b></font>

219
00:14:24,604 --> 00:14:27,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess miracles do happen.</b></font>

220
00:14:30,814 --> 00:14:32,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Wow!
--They're good.</b></font>

221
00:14:32,984 --> 00:14:36,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Every driver here has good skills.</b></font>

222
00:14:38,784 --> 00:14:40,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi?</b></font>

223
00:14:40,324 --> 00:14:43,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've never been to other passes, right?</b></font>

224
00:14:43,894 --> 00:14:45,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How was it?</b></font>

225
00:14:45,224 --> 00:14:49,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I mean, I wasn't the one driving,</b></font>

226
00:14:49,894 --> 00:14:51,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I really can't say.</b></font>

227
00:14:51,734 --> 00:14:55,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you sure? Your eyes were pretty serious.</b></font>

228
00:14:55,674 --> 00:14:57,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah?</b></font>

229
00:14:57,474 --> 00:14:59,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They look totally different now,</b></font>

230
00:14:59,804 --> 00:15:01,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as if you're a different person.</b></font>

231
00:15:01,974 --> 00:15:03,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Could you race here?</b></font>

232
00:15:03,814 --> 00:15:07,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wouldn't know until I tried it.</b></font>

233
00:15:07,314 --> 00:15:09,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--There!
--The Sileighty?!</b></font>

234
00:15:19,324 --> 00:15:22,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Continuous reverse drift!
--What the...?!</b></font>

235
00:15:24,334 --> 00:15:26,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>She's good!</i></b></font>

236
00:15:26,664 --> 00:15:30,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Did you see that?
--The narrow road made it intense!</b></font>

237
00:15:31,504 --> 00:15:35,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I told Mako that I was good at drifting,</i></b></font>

238
00:15:35,714 --> 00:15:39,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but I still panic when the rear slides out.</i></b></font>

239
00:15:39,984 --> 00:15:43,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I seriously have to work at it,</i></b></font>

240
00:15:43,354 --> 00:15:45,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>or I'll lose my angel!</i></b></font>

241
00:15:45,484 --> 00:15:48,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Let's head down.
--Yeah, okay.</b></font>

242
00:15:48,554 --> 00:15:52,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Every pass has a great racer.</b></font>

243
00:16:04,974 --> 00:16:08,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's going pretty fast, isn't he?</b></font>

244
00:16:08,344 --> 00:16:10,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We got three people here.</b></font>

245
00:16:10,344 --> 00:16:11,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't keep up.</b></font>

246
00:16:11,814 --> 00:16:14,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'd better give him some room.</b></font>

247
00:16:14,244 --> 00:16:17,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He seems out of sync,</b></font>

248
00:16:17,154 --> 00:16:19,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and his car's acting weird.</b></font>

249
00:16:19,554 --> 00:16:21,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How can you tell?</b></font>

250
00:16:21,724 --> 00:16:25,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not positive, but that's
probably what's going on.</b></font>

251
00:16:25,024 --> 00:16:26,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Probably?</b></font>

252
00:16:32,404 --> 00:16:35,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He spun out!</b></font>

253
00:16:35,374 --> 00:16:37,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi was right.</b></font>

254
00:16:39,844 --> 00:16:42,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Crap! A car's coming!</b></font>

255
00:16:51,184 --> 00:16:52,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was close!</b></font>

256
00:16:52,724 --> 00:16:55,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is this idiot?!</b></font>

257
00:16:55,354 --> 00:16:58,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As the rear slides out, he panics
and spins out of control.</b></font>

258
00:16:58,794 --> 00:17:01,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a beginner's mistake.</b></font>

259
00:17:01,934 --> 00:17:04,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, S13!</b></font>

260
00:17:04,094 --> 00:17:08,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Move out of the way, or you'll
put other drivers in danger!</b></font>

261
00:17:08,204 --> 00:17:10,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm moving...</b></font>

262
00:17:11,404 --> 00:17:13,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's so embarrassing!</b></font>

263
00:17:13,474 --> 00:17:16,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's act like we don't know him.</b></font>

264
00:17:17,474 --> 00:17:19,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry about that...</b></font>

265
00:17:37,394 --> 00:17:39,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's wrong?</b></font>

266
00:17:40,334 --> 00:17:42,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing.</b></font>

267
00:17:49,674 --> 00:17:55,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So, it's Mako whose Sileighty</i>
<i>is the fastest at Usui Pass.</i></b></font>

268
00:17:57,484 --> 00:17:59,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wanna die!</i></b></font>

269
00:18:03,294 --> 00:18:06,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--A day off?
--He hasn't called, either.</b></font>

270
00:18:06,694 --> 00:18:11,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is very rare for a workaholic like Iketani.</b></font>

271
00:18:11,104 --> 00:18:14,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He must've taken it real hard.</b></font>

272
00:18:14,364 --> 00:18:18,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He didn't say a word after
what happened last night.</b></font>

273
00:18:18,204 --> 00:18:20,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At a rest area on the way back,</b></font>

274
00:18:20,274 --> 00:18:22,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>his eyes were dull from shock.</b></font>

275
00:18:22,714 --> 00:18:26,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I felt too bad to say anything to him.</b></font>

276
00:18:26,484 --> 00:18:29,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I had a bad feeling about this.</b></font>

277
00:18:29,154 --> 00:18:32,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She was too cute to be his girlfriend.</b></font>

278
00:18:32,354 --> 00:18:35,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like I said, racers don't need girls.</b></font>

279
00:18:35,394 --> 00:18:39,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki the Lonely Driver... that's my title.</b></font>

280
00:18:39,524 --> 00:18:42,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hope he'll snap out of it soon.</b></font>

281
00:18:51,744 --> 00:18:54,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Telephone, Koichiro!</b></font>

282
00:18:54,874 --> 00:18:56,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tell them I'm sleeping...</b></font>

283
00:18:56,514 --> 00:18:59,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's probably Kenji.</b></font>

284
00:18:59,514 --> 00:19:03,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a girl named Mako Sato!</b></font>

285
00:19:13,164 --> 00:19:15,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did you want to talk to me?</b></font>

286
00:19:15,834 --> 00:19:17,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

287
00:19:17,264 --> 00:19:21,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you're here to make fun of me, please don't.</b></font>

288
00:19:21,034 --> 00:19:25,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I'm not here to make fun of you.</b></font>

289
00:19:25,374 --> 00:19:28,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I never suspected it was you.</b></font>

290
00:19:30,274 --> 00:19:36,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I saw your Sileighty drift
through the narrow road.</b></font>

291
00:19:36,514 --> 00:19:38,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The fastest at Usui Pass...</b></font>

292
00:19:40,724 --> 00:19:45,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You could've warned me about that.</b></font>

293
00:19:45,464 --> 00:19:47,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry.</b></font>

294
00:19:47,124 --> 00:19:49,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never told anyone about this.</b></font>

295
00:19:49,634 --> 00:19:51,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was shocking to me, too,</b></font>

296
00:19:51,864 --> 00:19:56,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and I realized that I owed you the truth.</b></font>

297
00:19:56,034 --> 00:19:58,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The truth?</b></font>

298
00:20:00,074 --> 00:20:03,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm really the quiet type.</b></font>

299
00:20:03,714 --> 00:20:06,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's hard to believe that a quiet type</b></font>

300
00:20:06,144 --> 00:20:08,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>could drift that dynamically.</b></font>

301
00:20:08,914 --> 00:20:16,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm one of those people whose
character changes behind the wheel.</b></font>

302
00:20:16,054 --> 00:20:18,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter how fast I drive,</b></font>

303
00:20:18,264 --> 00:20:21,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>men don't see me as girlfriend material,</b></font>

304
00:20:21,894 --> 00:20:27,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I've decided to put an end to this.</b></font>

305
00:20:28,004 --> 00:20:31,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm quitting racing after this summer.</b></font>

306
00:20:33,244 --> 00:20:35,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To make this summer memorable,</b></font>

307
00:20:35,144 --> 00:20:38,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I would like to race
Akina's Eight-Six at Usui Pass.</b></font>

308
00:20:38,944 --> 00:20:40,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wha...?</b></font>

309
00:20:40,584 --> 00:20:42,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's my wish.</b></font>

310
00:20:42,584 --> 00:20:46,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In return for my wish...</b></font>

311
00:20:46,984 --> 00:20:50,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I'll give you my virginity.</b></font>

312
00:20:51,664 --> 00:20:54,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait a minute! That's nonsense!</b></font>

313
00:20:54,764 --> 00:20:57,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Am I not good enough?
--That's not it.</b></font>

314
00:20:57,534 --> 00:20:59,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's my friend,</b></font>

315
00:20:59,834 --> 00:21:03,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I can't sell him out like that.</b></font>

316
00:21:04,704 --> 00:21:06,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I get it now.</i></b></font>

317
00:21:06,544 --> 00:21:08,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Her true intention...</i></b></font>

318
00:21:08,674 --> 00:21:11,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...was not me, but Takumi.</i></b></font>

319
00:21:11,844 --> 00:21:14,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Otherwise, a pretty girl like her</i></b></font>

320
00:21:14,684 --> 00:21:18,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>wouldn't be interested in someone like me.</i></b></font>

321
00:21:22,724 --> 00:21:24,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I understand.</b></font>

322
00:21:24,554 --> 00:21:26,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll do what I can.</b></font>

323
00:21:26,564 --> 00:21:30,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Really?
--Don't get me wrong, though.</b></font>

324
00:21:30,064 --> 00:21:34,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not doing this
because of your proposition.</b></font>

325
00:21:34,674 --> 00:21:36,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani...</b></font>

326
00:21:36,174 --> 00:21:40,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just want to make your wish come true.</b></font>

327
00:21:51,724 --> 00:21:54,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's okay...</i></b></font>

328
00:21:54,224 --> 00:22:00,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...because for a short while,</i>
<i>I was falling for her.</i></b></font>

329
00:22:00,264 --> 00:22:04,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I just want her to be happy.</i></b></font>

330
00:22:11,234 --> 00:22:15,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'd probably be laughed at for this,</i></b></font>

331
00:22:15,274 --> 00:22:18,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but I really liked her.</i></b></font>

332
00:22:18,714 --> 00:22:21,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I loved her...</i></b></font>

333
00:22:21,084 --> 00:22:23,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...even though I was mistaken.</i></b></font>

334
00:22:34,524 --> 00:22:40,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ai ni tsukare hate samayotteta koro</i></b></font>

335
00:22:40,364 --> 00:22:48,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yokubou dake ni kararete miushinatteita</i></b></font>

336
00:22:48,214 --> 00:22:54,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kimagure na unmei wa</i></b></font>

337
00:22:54,614 --> 00:23:02,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mujaki na hitomi ni miserarete yuku</i></b></font>

338
00:23:03,624 --> 00:23:10,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sake bara no you ni akaku</i>
<i>tsuyoku, tsuyoku kimi o daite</i></b></font>

339
00:23:10,164 --> 00:23:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Tatta hitotsu kono omoi o shinjitsu da to ieru</i></b></font>

340
00:23:16,974 --> 00:23:22,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yorokobi o kanadeyou...</i></b></font>

341
00:23:22,144 --> 00:23:29,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kagayaku mirai e</i></b></font>

342
00:23:41,194 --> 00:23:48,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kazoe kirenai hodo tashikame aou</i></b></font>

343
00:23:48,874 --> 00:23:54,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Jounetsu yo eien e todoke</i></b></font>

344
00:23:54,944 --> 00:24:01,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sake bara no you ni akaku</i>
<i>tsuyoku, tsuyoku dakishimete</i></b></font>

345
00:24:01,614 --> 00:24:08,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Tatoe nani o ushinattemo</i>
<i>kono ude o hanasanai</i></b></font>

346
00:24:08,454 --> 00:24:13,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Utsukushiku karen ni sake...</i></b></font>

347
00:24:13,694 --> 00:24:20,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kiseki no hana yo</i></b></font>

348
00:24:26,704 --> 00:24:30,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mako, how can you be interested in Iketani?</i></b></font>

349
00:24:30,374 --> 00:24:32,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't know...</i></b></font>

350
00:24:32,014 --> 00:24:34,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And you made that big proposition.</i></b></font>

351
00:24:34,484 --> 00:24:37,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Maybe that was a little too much...</i></b></font>

352
00:24:37,084 --> 00:24:39,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There're tons of good-looking guys,</i></b></font>

353
00:24:39,324 --> 00:24:41,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>so why Iketani?!</i></b></font>

354
00:24:41,754 --> 00:24:45,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But I kind of like him...</i></b></font>

355
00:24:45,094 --> 00:24:48,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--I really don't get it!</i>
<i>--Shush!</i></b></font>

